\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

true
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 probability of
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\overline{E}$
\end_inset

 can be anywhere in the range 
\begin_inset Formula $[0.7,0.8]$
\end_inset

